### 1. Save a New Department
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "department_name": "Computing",
  "department_location": "Building A - Floor 2"
}

### 2. Get All Departments
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/departments/all
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Department By ID (Using PathVariable)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/departments/1
Accept: application/json

### 4. Update Department
PUT http://localhost:8080/v1/departments
Accept: application/json